      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Yes — ER is valid in both TWL and SOWPODS. It scores just 2 points, but its real power lies in its tiles. E and R are two of the most common letters in the bag (12 E's and 6 R's), so you'll see ER opportunities constantly. As an interjection expressing hesitation ("er, I'm not sure..."), it's a legitimate word that helps manage your rack when common tiles pile up.</p>

